acquireKitty(uint256,address).author: @ugwu @ziweidream
acquireKitty(uint256,address).details: The last owner must be stored as a returned referenceThis function can only be carried out via proxy
acquireKitty(uint256,address).return: true if the acquisition was successful

becomeGhost(uint256,uint256).author: @ziweidream
becomeGhost(uint256,uint256).details: The kitty must be owned by the gameThis function can only be carried out via CronJobThis function will make a kitty permanently dead
becomeGhost(uint256,uint256).return: true if the kittie became a ghost and transferred to KittieHellDB

getKittyStatus(uint256).author: @ziweidream
getKittyStatus(uint256).return: the previous kitty owner, the kitty dead status, the kitty playing status, the kitty ghost status, and the kitty death time

getResurrectionCost(uint256,uint256).author: @ziweidream
getResurrectionCost(uint256,uint256).details: The resurrection cost per sec is a constant determined by GameVarAndFee contract

params._kittyID: The kitty for whom the resurrection cost is requested

isKittyDead(uint256).author: @ziweidream
isKittyDead(uint256).return: true/false if the kitty ID is dead or not

killKitty(uint256,uint256).author: @ziweidream
killKitty(uint256,uint256).details: This function can only be carried out via CronJOb
killKitty(uint256,uint256).return: true/false if the kitty ID is killed or not

params._kittyID: The kitty whose death time is requested

payForResurrection(uint256,uint256).author: @ziweidream
payForResurrection(uint256,uint256).details: The kitty must not be permanent deadThis function can only be carried out via proxyThe ressurection payment is in KTY tokens and sent to EndowmentFund contract
payForResurrection(uint256,uint256).return: true/false if the kitty ID is resurrected or not

devdoc.title: This contract is responsible to acquire ownership of participating kitties, keep the mortality status and permanent lock them if needed.

acquireKitty(uint256,address).notice: transfer the ownership of a kittie to this contract

userdoc.notice: This contract is able to lock kitties forever caution is advised
